{"tid":44260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母語教學已經係失敗同萬年遺毒","createTime":"2016-12-18T06:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T02:30:25.000Z","uid":8543,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd57bca9e590d30b288282c2b5625a5632fd5b5","tid":44260,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"點解上一代人要咁害我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821cc15064f5218dbae1b4df22322af6b8167c94","tid":44260,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"政府應該立法用英文做母語"},{"pid":"ce0d7aff39fcc5b7ab8d5e78bbad6a1639ad7eee","tid":44260,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"係咩？sor我英中"},{"pid":"538ae8cedcc5d4c16f30487f33c602b5fbb110a1","tid":44260,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咩？sor我英中</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry 我係失敗者"},{"pid":"52b9d8f582e2da3a064dfe0abbd6dae3b5bb0bf4","tid":44260,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:11:24.000Z","msg":"中中真係好小人入倒u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f80d4d78d40cccae694179c78bd3b323feb5b14","tid":44260,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中中真係好小人入倒u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知母語教育搞嚟做咩，大學就只會用英文做教育語言，咁學中文嚟托咩。完全莫名其妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc57f50c8f0bf38dcd73d940ed6fc6c9601a631","tid":44260,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"見到班人個陣支持<br />\n真係好想一拳閪落去"},{"pid":"881a81deb7070ddfdc1a11bdd4331d0beb73182c","tid":44260,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中中真係好小人入倒u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知母語教育搞嚟做咩，大學就只會用英文做教育語言，咁學中文嚟托咩。完全莫名其妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上到大學食撚哂屎<br />\n明明溫兩三個鐘既野，轉左英文<br />\n溫到死都係有野溫唔熟"},{"pid":"43c22ce432aa1cc1cceeb942decc4fd05c08d250","tid":44260,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中中真係好小人入倒u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知母語教育搞嚟做咩，大學就只會用英文做教育語言，咁學中文嚟托咩。完全莫名其妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上到大學食撚哂屎<br />\n明明溫兩三個鐘既野，轉左英文<br />\n溫到死都係有野溫唔熟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢大學如果都搞母語教學就話銜接到，只係中學搞但大學又唔搞，都唔知咩政策嚟。完全唔明白當年推的官員究竟點考慮。佢哋難道唔明白讀中學的唯一目的，其實就係讀大學？總之就好騎尼+古怪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92ff809a38f31aa5a6c5216e2b7b1cf6da14656","tid":44260,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"母語教學真係好毒既政策<br />\n香港係國際城市，英文廢等同廢左同外面接軌既能力"},{"pid":"85634c8eceeb1df319bc06d8d4751cd81ce509ff","tid":44260,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:53:33.000Z","msg":"要本土、港獨，又唔要母乳教育，算點？"},{"pid":"c6de2cff734ccefff9fc6c3f6385e28808d563e3","tid":44260,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB