中底幫中中補習都教死人<br />\n真心覺得佢地好慘"},{"pid":"ab350f1cdd7e2d52592302cb29b5ab9bd970fa9d","tid":44260,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解上一代人要咁害我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記得報牛"},{"pid":"359182d0d404a285636494452ff161c45545320e","tid":44260,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"母語教育更失敗地方<br />\n<br />\n港共迫香港仔用匪語做母語<br />\n用匪語學中文<br />\n<br />\n下場係，正體字唔撚識，英文都唔撚識，普通話唔撚識講。中文水平好似南亞人咁"},{"pid":"b232814410d800058d623eeaf08bbaf49a3b965e","tid":44260,"uid":54411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:19:26.000Z","msg":"曾經的 中中撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而家情願自己唔識中文、但有流利英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3260eea21aa2a4e7765c14209ce02efd3e807a","tid":44260,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"on9 ga係一邊力力地支持英語<br />\n一邊又力力地按底中文ga地位<br />\n合約 全部都會加多句以英文版本為准"},{"pid":"65e486323062e98f47e906eb9f3c9b513e76e2e2","tid":44260,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公道d講<br />\n母語教學係令大部分語文能力弱既學生都可以更加容易學習中學以下程度既知識<br />\n受惠既學生係比較多<br />\n至於覺得英文教係好d既人<br />\n其實一直都有英小同英中係度<br />\n你考得入既根本冇呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家就係硬生生損害咗我英文能力<br />\n唔見得中文教學有乜用<br />\n好似以前咁<br />\n不過加長中文堂咪得"},{"pid":"2c7db128a7487ef44475b11bc0a0965d0af61ecc","tid":44260,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公道d講<br />\n母語教學係令大部分語文能力弱既學生都可以更加容易學習中學以下程度既知識<br />\n受惠既學生係比較多<br />\n至於覺得英文教係好d既人<br />\n其實一直都有英小同英中係度<br />\n你考得入既根本冇呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然讀中學的唯一目的就係入大學，假如中學的教育模式係令個學生，較低機會入到大學。<br />\n<br />\n學唔學得好中學以下程度既知識，其實係毫無意義。因為中學層次的工作，冇幾多需要中學的知識，所謂的受惠更絕對難以成立。<br />\n<br />\n咩語言教都唔係問題。但大學就首崇英語。中小學就母語教育，然後釘死少數中小學，可以用英語教學。何來公道可言？變相等同政府自己本身都承認，母語教育的弊端。否則就冇必要分英小英中，然後仲搞微調。"},{"pid":"8fca37ca769e59636461b2298122fa34b16688bf","tid":44260,"uid":40681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:32:27.000Z","msg":"司徒華<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed5bb1d2cae7152abd7cc99be5d2acbb61d62db","tid":44260,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>母語教育更失敗地方<br />\n<br />\n港共迫香港仔用匪語做母語<br />\n用匪語學中文<br />\n<br />\n下場係，正體字唔撚識，英文都唔撚識，普通話唔撚識講。中文水平好似南亞人咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩語言都唔係問題，但應該有個統一的標準。唔好大學就只認英文，其他語言當9流，中小學就唔係呢個玩法，分埋咩中中/英中，咁的政策絕對唔正常唔合理。一係就大中小學都母語教育，一係就大中小學都全變英大/英中/英小先係。"},{"pid":"b66ba2dfcb477c0fe494105b9770f969e249ffaf","tid":44260,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要本土、港獨，又唔要母乳教育，算點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c86d1c96755a79df329e4b898a625932b06a11","tid":44260,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"而係...硬生生降低成個標準<br />\n真係有幫助咩？"},{"pid":"1a69964f7371ffb05de7cbd65cff37baec6dd8ba","tid":44260,"uid":24516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752bb92a94ce0222c1bf0fc075f59c2c7f001809","tid":44260,"uid":8543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7033c81d6ae6f30f3e8f384921b7d1dda4a711a6","tid":44260,"uid":13809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要本土、港獨，又唔要母乳教育，算點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本土既文化就係中英薈萃<br />\n睇怕你都係新腥港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818c48964507edb0a84f8531779156a433c8efea","tid":44260,"uid":54411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/220325_d914c9a1abe63decfdf270cbe382a049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F220325_d914c9a1abe63decfdf270cbe382a049.jpg&h=df7cccb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到呢到好大感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45374f11c07615b822708541e0149d50c9d94ab8","tid":44260,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f5b9358130cc60a71559e4013bc13d923a63c8","tid":44260,"uid":59648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>母語教育更失敗地方<br />\n<br />\n港共迫香港仔用匪語做母語<br />\n用匪語學中文<br />\n<br />\n下場係，正體字唔撚識，英文都唔撚識，普通話唔撚識講。中文水平好似南亞人咁</blockquote><br />\n我初中嗰陣中文用蝗語教，成日都聽唔明，都中文冇晒興趣，好彩到高中我啊sir都知死，用廣東話教，先明佢講咩"},{"pid":"abf296973d8f9201fbb317f642f6ee9ab12f20bf","tid":44260,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"等天收"},{"pid":"da64c1489eea3c13a1eb1c604bd3df0acc324bd3","tid":44260,"uid":9082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb49479fc53dc5094bcb7a00214e87c58387baef","tid":44260,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"39c91c932c58e3bcc4f638a51387a4f606a00acf","tid":44260,"uid":7698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"用中文學science 學埋啲5p字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576b0472667b4c0c268d67ba9ebce10a58ebe529","tid":44260,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用中文學science 學埋啲5p字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上到大學就會發覺到個差別，人地用30分鐘溫，你用3個鐘溫，佢仲高分過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港班垃圾官拎最高既人工，諗最弱智既政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81f97a92d921588be1d617d2558a7bc02c1853d","tid":44260,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"弱化政策<br />\n<br />\n有心要摧毀八九十後，因為八九十後對中共最具威脅"},{"pid":"83f23387ffd50b0207232fa0386c3a181648697b","tid":44260,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"最撚嚴重係行母乳教學但完全無成效，班90後00後中文水平唔見得有提高，英文又唔拖唔水，兩頭唔到岸 ，害撚死人"},{"pid":"23e4f5c314b72e7eb5869bfce595bb403f0a331e","tid":44260,"uid":66983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"屌咁蝗語教學呢？"},{"pid":"e47b0421475c87f226b658cb07e4f1718dc3fa87","tid":44260,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌咁蝗語教學呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更衰"},{"pid":"19d88e99b4627be94ded1b0b05763c56ba9875bc","tid":44260,"uid":1622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"我算係半個母語教育得益者又係半個受害者<br />\n<br />\n高中用英文讀全部跟唔上，全班最尾<br />\n後尾同老師講轉中文自己讀，全班頭幾<br />\n最後入左HKU，之後就...睇一份幾百既READING要睇成個鐘<br />\ntutorial諗到點用英文答個時人地已經答左第三題<br />\n<br />\n根本完全跟唔上，GPA只係岩岩好3<br />\n如果有一間用中文教既大學我一定去讀"},{"pid":"81ece381d67ed6be44c1b79cc9f651e2534dbfad","tid":44260,"uid":1622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"不過老實講我自己都唔係太明點解D人咁怕用英文讀理科<br />\nbio就唔洗講，中文學易10倍<br />\n但就算係chem，我覺得d中文都唔係咁奇怪姐<br />\n中文怪英文更怪，可能我有英文讀寫障礙...<br />\n<br />\n但係由英文讀變左用中文讀之後<br />\n高中d chem都係由全班最尾個幾個變到長期頭3<br />\n我花既時間係一樣(甚至少左因為唔需要花時間背英文字)<br />\n但回報係用英文讀既幾倍"},{"pid":"2dbcaff45d2e0623faac48d12064e47188c22346","tid":44260,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我算係半個母語教育得益者又係半個受害者<br />\n<br />\n高中用英文讀全部跟唔上，全班最尾<br />\n後尾同老師講轉中文自己讀，全班頭幾<br />\n最後入左HKU，之後就...睇一份幾百既READING要睇成個鐘<br />\ntutorial諗到點用英文答個時人地已經答左第三題<br />\n<br />\n根本完全跟唔上，GPA只係岩岩好3<br />\n如果有一間用中文教既大學我一定去讀</blockquote><br />\n你一定好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中中基本上除左英文堂會接觸到英文之外<br />\n係唔會識英文<br />\n上到大學全部講英文根本聽唔明"},{"pid":"3b1d0184bac391cca8872bc87be9f52cce1062f9","tid":44260,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T18:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚認同，入u之後真係食咗屎，根本變咗學英文時間多過學major d野"},{"pid":"f9af23220a24c8a461e22c95db1eca5c4e4a2cd5","tid":44260,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T18:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中中真係好小人入倒u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你連少同小都分唔到，又關中中事？"},{"pid":"75febab5b1fecd987f953b7ec81949464243d0a5","tid":44260,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"我中中<br />\n咪講入大學，依家都食緊屎"},{"pid":"4a7aac8c927a0e42918b4fb7b49bd50e3fdf2123","tid":44260,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T18:54:54.000Z","msg":"以前好多都係中英溝埋教<br />\n讀英文課本,寫英文essay,但係講書用中文<br />\n視學官黎就全班扮晒野轉英文channel<br />\n<br />\n呢種模式好處係英文爛船都有三分釘<br />\n特別係文科，hist,geog 呢d A level 都要寫essay，上堂自然會學到好多vocab，英文想肥都幾難<br />\n<br />\n壞處亦顯然易見，如果你最基本既英文唔掂，就會全部仆晒街<br />\n<br 